data.description:
Elegance meets functionality in this freshly painted all-brick ranch style residence featuring 3-bedroom 3  renovated baths, including a fourth bedroom in the basement for added versatility. Energy-efficient LED lights in the bedrooms. Walk on new LVP flooring throughout and experience culinary delight in the renovated kitchen featuring a stylish backsplash, new countertops, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. Additional treasures of this home - a BiG basement adorned with a bathroom, family room, and bedroom. Upstairs another family room with cozy fireplace. Enjoy the best of indoor and outdoor living with a sunroom and an attached 2-car garage, all seamlessly integrated into this charming home. The private backyard provides a serene escape, completing the perfect picture of comfortable and stylish living. Fresh interior and exterior paint add the final touch, making this residence a delightful blend of comfort and aesthetic charm.
This residence is not just a home; it's a masterpiece of modern living.
